dc_title_s: Philips' special large scale map of the North Western Frontier.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by spot heights and land forms. Includes 2 insets: "Military map of Indian Empire" and "Overland routes to India". 1 map: col.; 50 x 69 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
